    "is_free": true,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Show off your skills as you leap through diverse lands filled with deadly obstacles. Start on easy difficulty to master the movement mechanics before taking on tougher challenges.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You play as a wisp with the unique ability to wall-jump, which will help you dodge enemies and navigate hazards. This mobility is key to conquering the different areas. Play solo or team up in local co-op to tackle all levels together. Only one player needs to reach the checkpoint, with others being teleported to it automatically after it's reached. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Aim for the highest score in increasingly challenging levels, including hard boss levels. Your score will be based on several factors, such as time taken, total deaths, lives collected, and levels completed.<br><br>Wall jump will be present throughout the whole game. So learn and master them!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3183960/extras/19fe0fb2ec7acd9612b342e2ab89089e.poster.avif?t=1765019465\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3183960/extras/19fe0fb2ec7acd9612b342e2ab89089e.webm?t=1765019465\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3183960/extras/19fe0fb2ec7acd9612b342e2ab89089e.mp4?t=1765019465\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Don't forget to dodge enemies!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3183960/extras/c17d63eabf0d0ee3770381151768c3b6.poster.avif?t=1765019465\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3183960/extras/c17d63eabf0d0ee3770381151768c3b6.webm?t=1765019465\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3183960/extras/c17d63eabf0d0ee3770381151768c3b6.mp4?t=1765019465\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Complete challenges to obtain special skins for your character, emotes or accessories. Check Steam achievements and ingame achievement level for more.</p>",
